Detailed Description

FeatureItemContainerContentTableEntry: item_type: Type of Item (FeatureItem, ContextFeatureItem, FeatureItemContainer ...) container_table_entry: submenu, needed if the item type is a FeatureItemContainer applicaton_id: ApplicationID of application the Feature belongs to feature_id: FeatureID of Feature; icon_id: icon URI datum: Pointer to DataItem or pointer to PropertyDescriptor property_editor_id: PropertyID defining the Editor to edit a PropertyItem context_id: ContextID of this Item
